<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>質數搜索器</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <button id="primeSearchTab" class="tab active">質數搜索</button>
            <button id="primePhoneTab" class="tab">質數手機號碼</button>
            <button id="themeToggle" class="theme-toggle">切換主題</button>
        </nav>

        <div id="primeSearchPage" class="page active">
            <h1>連續質數序列搜索</h1>
            <form id="primeSearchForm">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="startRange">搜尋範圍：</label>
                    <input type="number" id="startRange" name="start" min="2" value="2" required>
                    <span>到</span>
                    <input type="number" id="endRange" name="end" min="2" max="100000" value="1000" required>
                    <span class="hint">（建議範圍：2-1000）</span>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="minSequences">序列數量：</label>
                    <input type="number" id="minSequences" name="min_sequences" min="1" value="1" required>
                    <span>到</span>
                    <input type="number" id="maxSequences" name="max_sequences" min="-1" value="5">
                    <span class="hint">（建議範圍：1-5，-1 表示無限制）</span>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="minLength">序列長度：</label>
                    <input type="number" id="minLength" name="min_length" min="2" value="2" required>
                    <span>到</span>
                    <input type="number" id="maxLength" name="max_length" min="-1" value="5">
                    <span class="hint">（建議範圍：2-5，-1 表示無限制）</span>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <p>此功能會尋找連續的質數序列，其和等於另一個質數。例如：</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>5 = 2 + 3（連續質數）</li>
                        <li>13 = 3 + 5 + 5（連續質數）</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>只有相鄰的質數才會被視為有效序列。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="form-actions">
                    <button type="submit" id="calculate" class="primary-button">計算</button>
                </div>
            </form>

            <div id="errorMessage" class="error"></div>
            <div id="progress" class="progress"></div>

            <div id="loading" class="loading-container">
                <div class="loading-spinner"></div>
                <div class="loading-text">計算中...</div>
            </div>

            <div id="results"></div>
        </div>

        <div id="primePhonePage" class="page">
            <h1>質數手機號碼</h1>
            <div id="prefixResults" class="prefix-results"></div>
            <form id="primePhoneForm">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="phonePrefix">手機號碼前綴：</label>
                    <div class="prefix-input">
                        <span class="fixed-prefix">09</span>
                        <input type="text" id="phonePrefix" name="prefix" pattern="[0-9]{2}" maxlength="2" placeholder="71" required>
                    </div>
                    <span class="hint">（請輸入 2 位數字）</span>
                </div>

                <div class="form-actions">
                    <button type="submit" class="primary-button">生成</button>
                </div>
            </form>

            <div id="phoneResults" class="phone-results"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="module" src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
